sql:
SELECT
id,
prop_name,
prop_address,
prop_postal,
land_size,
builtup,
tenure,
year_built,
`TOP`,
docuserid,
types,
kind,
hdb_town,
hdb_scheme,
cusid,
agentid,
photos,
land_size_unit,
builtup_unit
FROM properties
ORDER BY prop_address
name: properties
